# Enabling Event-driven Computation in Brain Dynamics

[//]: # (<p align="center">)

[//]: # (  	<img alt="Header image of brainevent." src="https://github.com/chaobrain/brainevent/blob/main/docs/_static/brainevent.png" width=50%>)

